description.V: *mumbling* What? Who knows what? I know what does, but he dozed unwisely! The Hermit of Awadji knows what's what, but what's left of him is I don't know where. But I do know what the Great Fire Djinn enjoys for lunch...mushroom kebabs! Aahahaha!

minidescription.V: Rescue the Hermit of Awadji from the Caverns of Living Fire. But be wary! He is being held captive by a Great Fire Djinn on Level 30.

completiondescription.V: Thanks to you Awadji has returned along with some of my sanity, but please give him time to recover from the ordeal. Upon returning from your next dungeon expedition, seek him near the obelisk.

incompletedescription.V: Erble Gerble What? I see no Awadji!

description.V: There's a Fire Crystal who's been stealing my chickens! Please help me! Do away with Kalza, and my livestock will be safe once again! I heard he lives on level 8 of The Caverns of Living Fire.

minidescription.V: Destroy Kalza the Fire Crystal on level 8.

completiondescription.V:
You have my thanks for defeating Kalza! - here is your reward!
You receive 2233 Experience 735 Fame 7330 Gold

incompletedescription.V: Please return when you have defeated Kalza.

questmonstername.V: The Shrine of Sworddrinker the Barbarous

description.V: One of the realm's spirits has been captured within The Shrine of Sworddrinker the Barbarous on the 9th level of The Caverns of Living Fire. You must activate the shrine and, while it recharges, defend it from the onslaught of summoned creatures. I'll give you this Gold Chain of Basics as reward!

minidescription.V: Activate the The Shrine of Sworddrinker the Barbarous on level 9 and defend it from waves of monster attacks until the timer expires. Your reward is a Gold Chain of Basics.

completiondescription.V:
Thank you for protecting the The Shrine of Sworddrinker the Barbarous. Here is your reward!
You receive 2579 Experience 805 Fame 10012 Gold
Gold Chain of Basics Received

incompletedescription.V: Please hurry and protect the The Shrine of Sworddrinker the Barbarous on level 9 !

description.V: Oh, my poor Elite Gel Herdlings! I didn't mean to fall asleep, but now they're scared and lost on the 11th level of The Caverns of Living Fire. Can you bring them home for me? Make sure you get all 9! I'll give you this Novice's Gold Ring of the Lizard as reward!

minidescription.V: Find 9 Elite Gel Herdlings on level 11. Your reward is a Novice's Gold Ring of the Lizard.

completiondescription.V:
Thank you for collecting all 9 of my Elite Gel Herdlings!
Novice's Gold Ring of the Lizard Received

incompletedescription.V: You have not yet found all 9 of my Elite Gel Herdlings.

name.V: Novice's Gold Ring of the Lizard

description.V: Yesterday, I sat upon a gilded throne, ruling all that you see as the mighty king of Ekbatan. I speak to you now as nothing more than a lowly beggar. You must lift this curse... if not for me, then for my kingdom. Redeem yourself, and restore our glorious city!

incompletedescription.V: Please return when the task is complete!
